('Pathway course requirement for entering students in College of Arts and Sciences and Leavey School of Business', 'All majors in the College of Arts & Sciences and Leavey School of Business who enter as first-year students (and transfer students with less than 44 units of transfer credit) must complete four Pathway courses (at least 16 units). If a Pathway includes courses worth less than four units, more than four courses will be necessary.', 'College of Arts and Sciences; Leavey School of Business', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Pathway course requirement for School of Engineering majors', 'All engineering majors must complete three Pathway courses (at least 12 units). If a Pathway includes courses worth less than four units, more than three courses will be necessary.', 'School of Engineering', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Pathway course requirement for transfer students with 44 or more units', 'Transfer students who matriculate with 44 or more units of transfer credit must complete three Pathway courses (at least 12 units). If a Pathway includes courses worth less than four units, more than three courses will be necessary.', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Completion at SCU', 'All courses counted toward the Pathway must be completed at Santa Clara University.', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Subject distribution limit', 'No more than the equivalent of two 4- or 5-unit courses may be in the same subject (e.g., ANTH, BIOL, ENGL, TESP). The remaining courses and units to complete the Pathway must be from a different subject (or subjects).', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Interdisciplinary exemption', 'Courses in ENVS, ETHN, CHST, PHSC, and WGST are exempt from the two-course-per-subject rule because they are inherently interdisciplinary.', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Sequence course limit', 'A Pathway may contain no more than two courses in either the Cultures & Ideas sequence (C&I 1, 2, 3) or the Religion, Theology, & Culture sequence (RTC 1, 2, 3).', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Foundations course limit', 'Only one course in a Pathway may be a Foundations course. (C&I 1 and 2 are Foundations courses; C&I 3 is not. RTC 1 is a Foundations course; RTC 2 and 3 are not.)', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('One Pathway per student', 'Students may complete only one Pathway, even if some courses would apply to multiple Pathways.', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Study abroad course limit', 'Students may apply no more than one study abroad course toward their Pathway.', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
('Approval requirement', 'Any course a student wants to include within a Pathway must have been approved for that Pathway. A list of approved courses is available on the Core website.', 'All', '["N/A"]', 'https://www.scu.edu/provost/core/integrations/pathways/guidelines-and-timeline/'),
